Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.07,0:03:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,多久了？\NHow long?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.57,0:03:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Eric？\NEric?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.71,0:03:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你说什么？（再说一遍）\NCan you repeat the question?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.21,0:03:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你病多久了？\NHow long have you been sick?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.91,0:03:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,第一迹象是在上个月表现出的\NSaw the first signs last month.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.25,0:03:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,那就是在圣彼得堡\NWhen you were in St. Petersburg.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.15,0:03:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,别表现得那么惊讶\NDon't act all surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.22,0:03:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我他妈的满地球找你\NI searched the whole fucking planet for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.92,0:03:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,圣他妈的圣彼得堡  Eric\NSaint fucking Petersburg, Eric?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.69,0:03:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道我有多讨厌俄国佬儿\NYou know how I hate the Russian people.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.40,0:03:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,额  我不知道你会找我\NWell, I didn't know you were gonna come looking for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.40,0:03:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,对  那你干嘛还到处跑？\NYeah, then why'd you keep on moving?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.44,0:03:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,恭喜你  Pam\NCongratulations, Pam.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.94,0:03:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你赢了\NYou've outwitted me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.78,0:03:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,但也只是因为我不舒服\NBut only because I'm not well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.22,0:03:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Tara不在了\NTara met the true death.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.09,0:03:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,昨晚我在摩洛哥时感应到的\NI felt it last night when I was in Morocco.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.89,0:04:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,她是我的后裔  Eric\NShe was my progeny, Eric.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.13,0:04:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你不说点儿什么吗？\NYou're not gonna say anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.60,0:04:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你玩那个游戏了？\NDid you play the bucket game?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.93,0:04:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,玩了\NI did.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.33,0:04:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,哦\NOh.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.40,0:04:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我喜欢那游戏\NI like the bucket game.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.61,0:04:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你到底怎么了？\NWhat is wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.14,0:04:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你他妈是Eric Northman\NYou are Eric fucking Northman.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.95,0:04:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你不能放弃  你得斗争\NYou don't give up. You fight.
