Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.18,0:06:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,（法语）对！\NOui!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.25,0:06:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了  Northman先生\NBravo, Mr. Northman.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.96,0:06:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你他妈是谁？\NWho the fuck are you?
