Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.51,0:07:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我不喜欢你\NI don't like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.92,0:07:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,这不公平  De Beaufort小姐\NThat's not fair, Miss De Beaufort.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.18,0:07:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,如果在别的情况下相见\NWere the circumstances of our meeting different,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.19,0:07:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我相信你我会成为朋友的\NI think you and I could've been friends.
