Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.49,0:07:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,但情况就是这样\NCircumstances are what they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.26,0:07:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你们太坏了  小伙姑娘啊\NYou've been bad, boys and girls,
