Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.11,0:08:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,没有Sylvie  事儿也能办成\NIt's no Sylvie, but it gets the job done.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.41,0:08:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,因为真血  主流即将成为现实\NWith Tru Blood, mainstreaming is going to become a reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.95,0:08:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,那日子该多无聊啊  无聊的想自杀\NAnd everyone lived bored and suicidally ever after.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.39,0:08:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,别卖萌了\NStop being cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.46,0:08:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,很多人或许喜欢你的微笑\NMany might appreciate your smile,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.59,0:08:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,但我向你保证  Yokonomo公司不会\Nbut I can assure you, the Yokonomo Corporation will not.
