Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.27,0:08:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我的任务就是确定你明白这点儿\NIt is my job to make sure you understand this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.78,0:08:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我懂了\NI understand.
