Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.22,0:10:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我们好好保护你吗？\Nhave I ever failed to protect you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.32,0:10:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,不是\NNo--
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.72,0:10:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你是我的后裔\NYou're my progeny.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.53,0:10:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你没必要和Flanagan小姐或者当局统一战线\NYou do not fall in line with Miss Flanagan or the Authority.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.53,0:10:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,听我的就是了\NYou fall in line with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.82,0:10:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿  Sook？\NHey, Sook?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.85,0:10:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我饿了  晚餐吃什么？\NI'm starving. What are you thinking for dinner?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.79,0:10:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿  冰箱里的牛排\NHey, those steaks in the freezer,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.93,0:10:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你认为那多久才能解冻？\Nhow long you think it'll take 'em to thaw?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.76,0:10:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Sook？\NSook?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.33,0:10:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿？\NHey?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.07,0:10:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我擦\NShit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.58,0:11:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,该死  Sookie\NGod damn it, Sookie.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.92,0:11:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Bill！  Bill！\NBill! Bill!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.25,0:11:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道她来这儿了！\NI know she came here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.85,0:11:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我能闻到她的味道！\NI can fuckin' smell her!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.99,0:11:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,狼人是这世上最好的追踪者\NWerewolves are the best trackers on the planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.33,0:11:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我掩盖了我们的行踪  Sookie\NI covered our tracks, Sookie.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.97,0:11:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Alcide不会找到我们的\NAlcide won't be finding us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.13,0:11:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,好  很好\NOkay, good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.17,0:11:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,现在和你谈这个会不会太迟了？\NIs it too late for me to talk you out of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.51,0:11:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么感觉不到我了？\NHow come you can't feel me anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.01,0:11:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我以为喝了你的血\NI thought once I'd had your blood,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.66,0:11:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,那便是永久\Nit was forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.51,0:11:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,在集中营\NAt that camp
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.10,0:11:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我喂养了所有的吸血鬼\Nwhere I fed all those vampires,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.79,0:11:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,几乎被吸干  Sookie\NI was completely drained, Sookie.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.56,0:11:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Jessica和James替我输血\NJessica and James may have saved my life
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.01,0:11:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,,才救了我\Nby transfusing me,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.62,0:11:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,如今的Bill Compton\Nbut the Bill Compton that I am today
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.93,0:11:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,和你血液里流淌的Bill Compton\Nhas nothing to do with the Bill Compton
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.63,0:11:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,已经没有任何关系了\Nwhose blood flows through your veins.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.67,0:11:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你是说你脱胎换骨了？\NSo you're saying you get a clean slate, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.30,0:12:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你已不再是那个\NThat you're not the same vampire
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.41,0:12:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,对我做出恐怖行为的吸血鬼了？\Nwho did all those horrible things to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.64,0:12:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,不\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.18,0:12:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,那些曾对你做过的事\NI have to live with the memories
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.08,0:12:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我会永远带着这些记忆活着\Nof what I'd done to you forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.58,0:12:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能除去任何罪责\NI can't acquit myself of any of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.09,0:12:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,很好\NGood.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.43,0:12:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我们要完成这个计划\NIf we're gonna go through with this plan,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.06,0:12:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,那你就得吸我的血\Nthen you're gonna have to take my blood
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.00,0:12:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,要不我帮不了你\Nor I won't be able to help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.62,0:12:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我有男朋友\NI have a boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.29,0:12:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得Rocky安全吗?\NDo you think Rocky's okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.02,0:12:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,恩  Wade  我确定\NYes, Wade, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.43,0:12:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你希望我妈妈没事儿吗？\NDo you think my mom's okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.93,0:13:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我真的这样期望\NI really hope so.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.01,0:13:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你认为我们都能平安无事吗？\NDo you think we're gonna be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.34,0:13:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,想知道个秘密吗？\NDo you want to know a secret?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.08,0:13:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你和我…\NYou and me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.88,0:13:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,曾经有过一次\Nwe made out once.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.66,0:13:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我会  我会记得这些的\NI would-- I would remember something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.36,0:13:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,不  我说真的  有吸血鬼\NNo, really. A vampire
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.64,0:13:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,对你迷魂了  但确有其事  我发誓\Nglamoured it outta you, but we did, I swear.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.36,0:13:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗？  我们曾经做过？\NReally? We really made out?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.33,0:13:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯哼\NUh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.10,0:13:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,这是这段儿我听到最好的消息了\NThis is the best news I've heard in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.45,0:13:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Adilyn！\NAdilyn!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.01,0:13:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,- Jessica! - 老爸来了  宝贝儿！\N- Jessica! - Andy: Daddy's coming, baby!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.95,0:13:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你们一起来了？ - 恩\N- You guys came together? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.12,0:13:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,别告诉他我们刚…\NDon't tell him that we were just about to--
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.65,0:13:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,- 别担心  我不会的  - 恩\N- Don't worry, I won't. - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.69,0:14:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,- 谁对你做的这些？ - 我们试着阻止他们\N- Who did this to you? - We tried to stop 'em,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.96,0:14:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,但他们拿走了所有的枪支弹药\Nbut they took all your guns, all your ammo,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.75,0:14:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,一切东西\Neverything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.26,0:14:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,- 谁做的？  - 我不知道  都有\N- Who did? - I don't know, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.47,0:14:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,整个镇子  就连Rocky也是其中一员\NThe whole town. Even Rocky was part of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.77,0:14:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,别让他惹上麻烦\NDon't get him in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.27,0:14:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,孩子  我们都有麻烦了\NSon, we're all in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.64,0:14:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,等等  他们去找谁了？\NWait, who are they after?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.44,0:14:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,他们去找每一个\NThey're after anyone and anything
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.86,0:14:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,和他们不一样的人或物\Nthat's different than they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.55,0:14:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,- 恩哼  - 你用最简单的\N- Uh-huh. - You take the simplest,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.75,0:14:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,每天你都会做的事\Nmost everyday thing you do...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.72,0:14:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,这些人…这些人曾只是\NThese people-- these people were just
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.73,0:14:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,坐下来等着吃个披萨夜宴\Nsitting down for a frozen pizza dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.13,0:14:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,假如那是你生命里\NWhat if that was the last thing
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.27,0:14:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,最后一件事情呢？\Nyou were ever gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.54,0:14:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,因为生活不会是只吃一半披萨\N'Cause life is supposed to add up to something,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.81,0:14:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,它是事情叠叠加加\Nnot be some half-eaten slice of pizza.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.38,0:14:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,他们抓走了我的未婚妻  牧师\NAnd they got my fiance, Reverend.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.95,0:14:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道\NI know they do, Sam.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.42,0:14:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你们掳走了我的未婚妻和未出世的孩子\NThey got my fiance and my unborn child,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.05,0:15:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我的人生才刚刚加入新元素啊\Nand my life is just startin' to add up to something,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.22,0:15:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能…\Nand I can't--
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.09,0:15:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,现在你…你要救他们回来\NNow you-- you're gonna get 'em back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.39,0:15:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你会见到你的孩子\NYou're gonna meet that baby of yours,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.72,0:15:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,但你得有信心（也指信仰）\Nbut you've got to have faith.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.99,0:15:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,牧师  他们到处都是耶稣啊\NReverend, they had Jesuses everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.36,0:15:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,墙上也是\NThey had Jesuses on the walls,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.16,0:15:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,每间卧室的壁炉架上都画耶稣\Nthey had Jesuses on the mantel in every single bedroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.57,0:15:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,他们有信仰\NThey had faith.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.04,0:15:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,那又有什么用？\NWhat good did it do 'em?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.31,0:15:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,那到底又有什么用啊？\NWhat good would not having had it done them?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.48,0:15:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道  我不知道\NI don't know. I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.11,0:15:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,至少他们不会对死亡将至的现实\NAt least they wouldn't have been blind to the fact
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.60,0:15:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,充耳不闻\Nthat death was coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.75,0:15:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,看看现在  我可不会在众人面前\NNow looky here, this ain't the kind of thing
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.99,0:15:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,说这些事儿的\NI say in front of a congregation,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.49,0:15:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,但这会儿就你和我\Nbut since it's just you and me right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.62,0:15:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,死亡…那…\Ndeath-- whew--
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.43,0:15:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,那个暗黑的混帐东西\Nis a dark and blinding motherfucker,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.56,0:15:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,不管你看不看得见他的到来\Nwhether you see it coming or you don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.36,0:15:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,人生都荒废在迎它的路上了\NBut a life spent in anticipation of it coming,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.57,0:15:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Sam  好吧  那不是该有的人生\NSam, well, that's not a life worth living.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.04,0:15:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Daniel牧师  抱歉打扰你\NReverend Daniels, I am so sorry to interrupt you,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.84,0:15:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,- 但是她又发狂了  - Tara！Tara！\N- but she is freaking out again. - Tara! Tara!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.28,0:15:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你都做了什么 Willa？\NWhat'd you do, Willa?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.81,0:15:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,又给了她点儿血\NI gave her more blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.71,0:16:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Tara  你去哪儿？\NTara, where'd you go?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.55,0:16:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉妈妈你在哪儿！\NTell Mama where you at!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.98,0:16:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Lettie Mae! Lettie Mae!\NLettie Mae! Lettie Mae!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.85,0:16:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你不是Tara！ - 我知道  亲爱的\N- You ain't Tara! - I know, honey.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.09,0:16:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,她受伤了\NShe was hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.77,0:16:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道还能做什么  对不起\NI didn't know what else to do. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.39,0:16:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  镇长先生  很抱歉\NAll right, Mr. Mayor, I'm sorry,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.51,0:16:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我能请你们都离开吗？\Nbut could I ask you all to leave?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.69,0:16:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托了  请离开吧  谢谢你们\NPlease, please leave. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.56,0:16:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,好  冷静点儿  看着我\NOkay, now calm down. Look at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.80,0:16:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,听我说  现在  我们…\NListen to me. Now, what did we--
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.56,0:16:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,- Tara！ - 不  不！\N- Tara! - No, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.10,0:16:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,- 冷静点  嘘 - Tara Tara\N- Hold on. Shh. - Tara, Tara.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.10,0:16:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,- Lettie Mae 有我呢  - Tara\N- Lettie Mae, stay with me. - Tara.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.94,0:16:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,额  真尴尬\NWell, that was awkward.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.64,0:16:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,恩  确实\NYeah, it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.44,0:16:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,牧师有的忙了\NThe Reverend's got his hands full.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.94,0:16:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,- Matt？ - 怎么  镇长先生？\N- Matt? - Yes, Mr. Mayor?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.65,0:16:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你可真是吸血鬼的菜啊  不是吗？\NYou're awful dishy for a vampire, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.48,0:16:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,就聊聊天嘛\NJust trying to make conversation.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.76,0:16:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,哇噢 这他妈又演哪儿出？\NWell, ain't this fucking perfect?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.68,0:17:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你们都在这儿干什么？\NWhat are y'all doing out here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.18,0:17:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,夺回小镇\NTaking our town back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.42,0:17:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,就你们  恩？\NYou are, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.25,0:17:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,确实\NIndeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.59,0:17:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,对\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.02,0:17:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你告诉他们了？ - 没错他说了\N- You told 'em? - Damn right he told us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.56,0:17:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我就知道你有问题\NI knew there was something off about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.19,0:17:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,现在终于明白了\NNow I know what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.00,0:17:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你是警察 Kenya  我是你的镇长\NYou're a cop, Kenya. I'm your mayor.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.30,0:17:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,就是说  你是黑人  他是白人\NTranslation-- you black, he's white.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.47,0:17:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,哦  我懂了  姑娘\NOh, I got it, girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.00,0:17:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿  Rocky  你听我说\NHey, Rocky, you listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.91,0:17:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你想救你妈妈回来吗  那就过来\NYou want to get your mom back, you come with me
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.08,0:17:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,因为这样救不了她\N'cause this ain't helpin' her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.41,0:17:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,当然能  我们有枪\NSure, it is. We got guns.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.81,0:17:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你想赌赌谁才安全吗  恩？\NHow much you wanna bet who's safer, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.21,0:17:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的枪能干掉那些吸血鬼\NOur guns against your fag vampire.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.38,0:17:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿  你是…\NHey, who you-- -
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.59,0:17:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,该死的  Vince！\NGod damn it, Vince!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.22,0:17:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,- 对  我们才安全  没错  - 对\NYeah, we're safer, all right. - Man: Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.59,0:17:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,不  Merlotte镇长  去你丫的\NNo, Mayor Merlotte, God damn you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.73,0:17:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你欺骗了良辰镇的善男信女\NYou tricked the fine men and women of Bon Temps
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.83,0:18:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,让他们以为投选出一个人类\Ninto thinking they were voting for a human being
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.10,0:18:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,而真相却是他们选出来的是个恶魔\Nwhen the truth is they were voting for the Devil.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.64,0:18:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你说啊  Gibson镇长\NYou tell him, Mayor Gibson.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.81,0:18:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,人民有发言权\NThe people have spoken.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.07,0:18:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我现在才是镇长\NI'm the mayor now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.41,0:18:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,作为镇长  我建议你现在回家\NAnd as mayor, I'm advising you to go on home,
