Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.42,0:18:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,好  那抱歉了  各位\NWell, I'm sorry, y'all,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.12,0:18:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,但我属于这儿\Nbut I belong here.
