Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.43,0:18:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,知道吗  我想过的\NYou know, I've been thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.20,0:18:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我们熬过这关\NIf we ever make it through this,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.20,0:18:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你会考虑\Nwould you ever consider
