Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.11,0:18:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你他妈在开玩笑吗？\NAre you fucking kidding me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.01,0:18:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你不行  但我们可以领养\NI know you can't make babies, but we could adopt.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.65,0:18:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我就是觉得  经过这一切\NI just feel, with everything going on...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.52,0:18:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,没家的男人一无是处\Na man ain't nothing without a family.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.56,0:19:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么？\NWhat?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.40,0:19:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,一个遍布死人的小镇\NOne town of dead people
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.07,0:19:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么就把你变成一个娘炮了？\Nand you're gonna let it turn you into a girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.24,0:19:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我  娘炮？\NMe, a girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.54,0:19:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,在我的年代  一个男人\NIn my day, when men marched to a village
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.06,0:19:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,走进一个被焚毁的小镇\Nthat was burned to the ground
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.21,0:19:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,目睹妇孺被烧焦的遗骸\Nand bore witness to the charred remains
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.92,0:19:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,战争将他们抛掷脑后\Nof women and children that war leaves in its wake,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.45,0:19:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你认为他们还会多想吗？\Ndo you think they gave it a second thought?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.65,0:19:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,他们不会\NThey didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.19,0:19:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,他们什么都不想  也不会感知其他\NThey didn't think anything. They didn't feel anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.59,0:19:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,因为那时  男人都是战士\NBecause back then, men were warriors.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.06,0:19:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯哼  好吧  我不想告诉你  Violet\NMm-hmm. Well, I hate to break it to you, Violet,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.57,0:19:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,但我是现代男性\Nbut I'm a modern man.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.53,0:19:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我会想  会感知\NI think and I feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.57,0:19:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我他妈还依旧是个战士\NAnd I'm still a badass motherfucker of a warrior.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.51,0:19:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我遇见你时\NYou were when I met you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.67,0:19:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,那天他们将你丢进我牢里\NThat day when they threw you into my cell,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.48,0:19:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,当然  你是有点身心疲废\Nsure, you were a little broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.41,0:19:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,但我还是很直白的说你是个男人\NBut I could tell right away that you were a man
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.61,0:19:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,就像从前的人\Nlike they used to make them,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.52,0:19:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,有原则的活着\Nwho lived by a code.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.28,0:20:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,有荣誉  有尊严的人\NWho had a sense of honor and dignity
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.72,0:20:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,如铁铸般锻造\Nand an iron-forged cock.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.06,0:20:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,这才是我爱的男人\NThat's the man I fell for.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.59,0:20:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,草你妹的现代人\NFuck being modern.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.03,0:20:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,- Jason?  - Stackhouse!\NJason? - Andy: Stackhouse!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.23,0:20:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我和Jason正在打嘴架\NJason and I are in the middle of a fight,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.78,0:20:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你丫识相滚开\Nso fuck off.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.70,0:20:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Stackhouse  我们有麻烦了\NStackhouse, we got a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.51,0:20:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,能进来吗？\NCan we come in?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.00,0:20:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,恩  进来吧\NYeah, come on in.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.24,0:20:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿  发生什么了？\NHey, what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.09,0:20:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,不准再向前  懂吗？\NNot one step further, got that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.98,0:20:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我的房子\NThis is my house.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.05,0:20:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Vince和他的同党\NVince and all his yahoos
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.22,0:20:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,冲进警局  偷走了所有枪支\Nbroke into the station, stole all our guns.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.35,0:20:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,他们怎么说服Kenya的？\NHow'd they get past Kenya?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.91,0:20:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Kenya也是其中一员\NKenya's one of 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.22,0:20:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,哦  该死\NOh, shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.12,0:20:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,是你来告诉他  还是我来？\NDo you wanna tell him or should I?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.32,0:20:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉我什么？\NTell me what?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.96,0:20:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,说啊\NWhat?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.96,0:20:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Adilyn担心他们在找Sookie\NAdilyn's afraid that they might be after Sookie.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.93,0:20:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,别担心  Stackhouse\NDon't worry, Stackhouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.30,0:20:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不会让她有事的\NWe ain't gonna let nothing happen to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.20,0:20:47.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我能让Adilyn和Wade躲在这里\NIt all right if I let Adilyn and Wade
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.90,0:20:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,随后再来接他们吗？\Nhole up here till I can come back for 'em?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.23,0:20:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,恩  当然\NYeah, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.80,0:20:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,别出去\NDo not go outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.74,0:20:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,别给任何人开门\NDo not open the door for anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.22,0:20:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我可不在附近\NI'm not fucking around.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.24,0:20:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,她不会听我的\NShe won't listen to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.09,0:20:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,但是  Wade  你得听话\Nbut, Wade, you better.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.64,0:20:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我们这样说定了\NI'll make you a deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.51,0:21:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我们在找到Sookie前休战怎么样？\NHow about we call a truce until we find Sookie?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.51,0:21:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,好  可以\NOkay, fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.58,0:21:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,但我不认为我们之间有什么问题\NBut I didn't realize that we still had a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.75,0:21:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,这种盲目乐观的态度只会让我讨厌你\NIt's "Pollyanna" Shit like that that makes me hate you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.45,0:21:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,好了  各位  出发吧\NAll right, y'all, let's do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.66,0:21:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,爆他丫的\NFuckin' A.
