Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.56,0:21:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了  夕阳西下了？\NWhat's wrong, Sundown?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.18,0:21:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你不喜欢我煮的菜吗？\NDon't you like what I was cooking?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.70,0:21:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,还有大麻吗？\NGot any more of that weed?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.26,0:21:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,木  没有了\NNope, no more weed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.33,0:21:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,昨晚都抽光了\NSmoked me clean out last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.20,0:22:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,但如果你一起\NBut I'll bust out the pharmacy
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.11,0:22:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我会去药房买\Nif you wanna join.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.67,0:22:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,希望可以  但吸血鬼不能吞药\NI wish I could, but vampires can't swallow pills.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.04,0:22:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  见鬼\NWell, damn.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.95,0:22:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,永生也并没标榜的那么好\NImmortality's not all it's cracked up to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.32,0:22:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,恩啊\NHmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.45,0:22:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我来问你\NLet me ask you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.22,0:22:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,现在  我知道我在逃避什么\NNow, I know what I was escaping from,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.06,0:22:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,但你心里在逃避什么呢？\Nbut what's on your mind that you want off?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.59,0:22:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我猜  就Jessica的烂事儿\NJust Jessica shit, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.73,0:22:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,关于Jessica的哪种事情呢?\NAny particular kind of Jessica shit?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.86,0:22:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,可以长篇大论的那种\NThere's a longer version of this conversation,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.50,0:22:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,但我没那心情\Nbut I'm not really in the mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.53,0:22:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,简而言之的呢\NThe shorter version goes something like--
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.60,0:22:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我们住一起  睡在彼此身边\Nwe live together, we sleep next to each other,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.14,0:22:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,时而来一炮\Noccasionally we fuck,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.44,0:22:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,但我不确定她是否真的走心了\Nbut I'm not so sure she even knows I'm there.
