Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.78,0:22:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,或许她才是漫不经心的那个\NMaybe she's the one who ain't there.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.55,0:22:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,- 恩  也许  - 大概\N- Hmm, maybe. - Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.52,0:22:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,但是长篇大论的话\NBut that's the longer version.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.96,0:22:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,记得你上次吞的什么药吗？\N'Member what it was, the last pill you took?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.36,0:23:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,吐诺尔（镇静剂或催眠药，商标名）\N- Tuinal. - Tuinal?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.03,0:23:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,- 嗯哼  - 恩\N- Mm-hmm. - Mm.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.70,0:23:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我可没机会尝试  感觉如何？\NI never had the chance. How was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.90,0:23:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,哦  它仿佛让你置身海洋\NOh, it turns your body into an ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.04,0:23:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,海洋啊\NOcean.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.51,0:23:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,让你的意识乘风逐浪\NAnd lets your consciousness ride that wave.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.65,0:23:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,哦  我要来吞一颗吐诺尔\NOoh, I'm gonna make me a Tuinal.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.05,0:23:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你又不能吞  - 当然  你能\N- You can't make a Tuinal. - Sure, you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.69,0:23:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,古今药物都是一个样儿\NToday's drugs are just like drugs back in your day.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.16,0:23:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,只不过现在被解构了\NExcept they've been deconstructed.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.66,0:23:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,化整为散  支离凌乱\NThey separate out the parts of the whole into pieces.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.16,0:23:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,现在他们这么命名\NNow they call them this,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.11,0:23:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,那么称呼  随它吧\Nthat, or whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.90,0:23:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,而我只用拿这个\NAnd all I gotta do is take this,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.16,0:23:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,选那个  无所谓\Nthat, or whatever
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.20,0:23:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,然后整一起\Nand put it together.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.30,0:23:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,在你知道前\NAnd before you know it,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.91,0:23:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,就可以通过吐诺尔随浪逐波了\Nyou're gonna be riding that Tuinal wave
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.07,0:23:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,就像是回到你所喜爱的童年时光\Njust like you did back in your love child days.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.58,0:23:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,如我所说  我不能再吞药了\NLike I said, I can't swallow pills anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.91,0:23:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,那我来\NI'll do the swallowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.95,0:23:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,给我20分钟\NJust give 'em 20 minutes
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.83,0:23:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,让它们融入我的血管\Nto get to know each other in my bloodstream,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.95,0:23:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我就能带你漫步海滩\Nthen I'm gonna take you to the beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.19,0:24:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我们下边还有多少？\NHow many more we got left down there?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.60,0:24:01.49,Default,,0,0,0,,四个人\NFour.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.49,0:24:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你把那个孕妇当一个还是两个？\NAre you counting the pregnant lady as one or two?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.33,0:24:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,加上孩子  就五个\NCounting the baby, we've got five.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.53,0:24:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我数学烂透了  那这是几天的食物？\NI'm shit at math. How many more days of food is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.63,0:24:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,拜你所赐  最多两天\NTwo max, thanks to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.34,0:24:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,听着  我们还得再回去一次\NLook, we're just gonna have to go back out there again.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.34,0:24:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,什么？不  我不去\NWhat? No, I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.95,0:24:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我没那个精力了\NI don't have the energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.01,0:24:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你以为我有吗？  我们没得选\NYou think I do? We ain't got no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.11,0:24:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,他们有吸血鬼保护着  真的\NThey've got vampires protecting them, they do.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.74,0:24:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我们都知道\NAnd we know that now.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.58,0:24:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要带着银链  木桩\NWe'll bring silver chains, stakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.21,0:24:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,不会有事的\NIt'll be all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.55,0:24:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我每隔一小时都得吃东西\NI have to eat every hour on the hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.22,0:24:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,假如我们出去\NWhat happens if we go out there
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.14,0:24:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,却没有找到任何人呢?\Nand we don't find anybody?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.32,0:24:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,那就带一个和我们一起去捕猎\NWe'll bring one of them out there hunting with us, then.
