Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.47,0:33:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,只是他们不肯上钩\NIt's just them not taking the bait
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.87,0:33:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,让人有点泄气而已\Nis a little insulting, is all.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.28,0:33:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我以为我的气味很特别\NI thought I smelled special.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.41,0:33:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,哦  确实\NOh, you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.22,0:33:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H00FFFF&\fn隶书\fs24\pos(364,44)}六旗：世界上最大的过山车主题公园
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.22,0:33:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你有去过六旗吗?\NHave you ever been to Six Flags?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.09,0:33:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能说有那种荣幸\NI cannot say that I've had the pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.96,0:33:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,那不是关闭了吗?\NDidn't they close that down?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.62,0:33:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,大概是在五六年前吧\NLike, five or six years ago, I think it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.73,0:33:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,但我爷爷曾经在我九岁生日那天\NBut my grandpa took me and Jason there once
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.53,0:33:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,带我跟Jason去过\Nfor my ninth birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.07,0:33:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,总之  他们有种像是自由落体的东西\NAnyway, they had this ride, like a free-fall thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.60,0:33:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道的  就是把你关在笼子里\Nyou know, where they put you in this cage
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.71,0:33:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,然后将你推出高台\Nand then they push you out over this ledge
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.21,0:33:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,抛向空中几百尺高\Nhundreds of feet up in the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.38,0:33:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你那时九岁?\NYou were nine?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.08,0:33:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我是说  虽然我是不朽的  但那也把我给吓死了\NI mean, I'm immortal and that would scare me to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.25,0:33:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,下落还不是最糟的\NThe fall wasn't the worst part.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.72,0:33:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,而是置空时\NIt was the waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.99,0:34:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道它们会把你抛下去\NYou knew they were gonna drop you,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.26,0:34:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,只是不知道是什么时候\Nyou just didn't know when.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.73,0:34:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,这确实是切身感受\NThat's exactly what this feels like.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.84,0:34:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你应该上战场试试\NYou should try going to war.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.31,0:34:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,这是战争吗  Bill？\NIs this war, Bill?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.48,0:34:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,是\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.18,0:34:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,没错  我想是\NYeah, I suppose it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.55,0:34:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,嘘  嘘\NShh. Shh.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.12,0:34:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想这样做\NI don't wanna do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.22,0:34:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,这是为你父亲的  Sarah\NIt's for your father, Sarah.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.06,0:34:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,这样他可以走时  有张照片作为留念\NSo he has a picture to remember us by while he's away.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.33,0:34:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,过来\NCome here.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.90,0:34:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你害怕吗？\NAre you frightened?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.50,0:34:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,是的  父亲\NYes, Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.24,0:34:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,怕什么？  相机吗？\NWhat of, the camera?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.44,0:34:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,- 不  - 那  是什么？\N- No. - Well, what, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.48,0:34:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你必须走吗？\NDo you have to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.35,0:34:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,亲爱的  我们说过的\NDarlin', we discussed this.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.48,0:34:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,那你会回来吗？\NAre you going to come home?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.59,0:35:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,是  当然会  亲爱的\NYes, of course I am, darlin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.32,0:35:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,那你为什么还需要一张照片？\NThen why do you need the photograph?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.56,0:35:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,这样…\NSo...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.13,0:35:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,当我想你们的时候  我就可以看到你\NI can look at you and your mother and your brother
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.00,0:35:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你妈妈  还有弟弟\Nwhen I'm feeling lonesome for ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.43,0:35:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,- 这不一样  - 对  是不一样\N- It won't be the same. - No, it won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.64,0:35:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,但比见不到你们好多了啊\NBut it'll be a lot better than not being able to see you at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.91,0:35:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,下一个？\NNext?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.41,0:35:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我有主意了\NI have an idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.01,0:35:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,- 请问您贵姓？ - Fortenberry 先生\N- May I ask your name? - Fortenberry, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.38,0:35:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我是Julian Fortenberry\NJulian Fortenberry.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.25,0:35:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Fortenberry先生  请问\NMr. Fortenberry, might I ask whether
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.05,0:35:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,能否先拍张我和我女儿的合影\Nyou would photograph myself and my daughter first,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.99,0:35:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,然后再拍全家福呢？\Nand then we can do the rest of my family after?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.83,0:35:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,额  你也看到了  我这儿锡料不多\NWell, I have only so many tins, you see,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.63,0:35:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,而且它们很贵\Nand they're quite expensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.10,0:35:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,恩  很乐意支付费用\NWell, I will gladly pay the cost.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.06,0:35:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托了  求你了\NPlease, I beg you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.60,0:35:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,恩  我想这也没什么大不了\NWell, I suppose there's no harm in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.50,0:35:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,- 这边请  先生  - 谢谢你  先生\N- Right this way, sir. - Thank you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.97,0:35:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,请您坐在那张椅子上\NIf you'd just take your mark on that chair right there, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.34,0:36:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,现在  保持姿势不动\NNow, we'll need to be very still.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.21,0:36:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,这是给你留念\NThis one's for you to keep.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.38,0:36:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,三 二 一  别动\NIn three, two, one, freeze.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.03,0:36:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,真有爱  现在是妈妈和宝宝\NLovely. And now mother and baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.43,0:36:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你要我…\NYou would like me...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.86,0:36:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,就坐在那张椅子上\NIn that chair right there
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.56,0:36:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,那就太好了  谢谢你  贵姓…\Nwould be wonderful, thank you, Mrs., uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.63,0:36:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Compton\NCompton.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.97,0:36:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,真是个有爱的家庭  Compton先生\NYou have a beautiful family, Mr. Compton.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.51,0:36:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你  先生\NThank you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.17,0:36:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,现在  保持姿势\NNow, very still.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.21,0:36:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,三 二 一  别动\NIn three, two, one, freeze.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.12,0:36:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Sookie\NSookie...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.79,0:36:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我等够了\NI'm sick of waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.62,0:36:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,来啊  你们\NCome on, y'all!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.73,0:36:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我尝起来阳光与花香同在\NI taste like sunshine and flowers
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.56,0:36:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我他妈的就在这里！\Nand I'm right fuckin' here!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.37,0:37:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,她睡着了吗?\NIs she asleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.17,0:37:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,终于  是的\NFinally, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.21,0:37:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,之前真对不起\NI'm so sorry about before.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.21,0:37:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,这不是你的错  Willa\NIt ain't your fault, Willa.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.58,0:37:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你真认为她是有意烫伤自己的吗?\NDo you really think she burned herself on purpose?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.25,0:37:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,上帝造我们的时候  Willa\NWhen the good Lord made us, Willa,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.72,0:37:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,让我们万事皆有因\NHe gave us reflexes for a reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.12,0:37:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,就连水都知道烧滚时要沸腾\NEven water knows to jump off a griddle when it's hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.32,0:37:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你饿了吗? - 我能挨到明天\N- You hungry? - I can wait until tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.49,0:37:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,不不不  甜心  不  不\NNo, no, no, sweetheart. No, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.43,0:37:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧  靠过来\NGo on, scoot over.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.10,0:37:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你确定?  你是牧师\NAre you sure? You're a reverend.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.50,0:37:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我确定\NI'm sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.95,0:37:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,啊\NAh.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.06,0:37:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,就在我一生最糟的事后\NI moved to this town
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.36,0:37:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我搬到了这个小镇\Nafter the worst period of my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.20,0:38:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我和我的第一任妻子\NMy first wife and I had--
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.97,0:38:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,失去了最年幼的女儿\Nwe had lost our youngest daughter
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.90,0:38:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,那持续了六个月\Ngoing on six months before,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.00,0:38:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,而那…\Nand it had--
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.88,0:38:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,毁了我们\Nit destroyed us.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.51,0:38:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我的妻子Tanya  她…\NMy wife Tanya, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.75,0:38:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,误入迷途\Nshe strayed.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.32,0:38:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,而我…\NAnd I...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.22,0:38:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,失去信仰\NI lost all faith...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.02,0:38:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,对上帝  对众生  还有我的婚姻\Nin God, people, in my marriage...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.20,0:38:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,以及自我\Nand in myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.50,0:38:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,邻居和会众\NNeighbors and congregates,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.82,0:38:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,他们带着拌菜或派\Nthey'd come by
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.37,0:38:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,前来会访\Nwith casseroles or pies
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.90,0:38:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,或只是要想看看我的情况\Nor just to check up on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.74,0:38:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,但你看  我会假装自己不在\NBut you see, I would pretend I wasn't there.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.18,0:38:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我会拉起窗帘  关掉电视\NI'd have the curtains drawn and the television off.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.39,0:38:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,躲在屋角\NI'd be cowering in a corner...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.02,0:39:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,试着屏住呼吸  害怕有人\Ntrying to hold my breath for fear that someone
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.29,0:39:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,和我说话\Nwould talk to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.30,0:39:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,跌入低谷\NI was low.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.90,0:39:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,而后一日清晨  醒来扣好衣领\NAnd then one morning, I woke up, put on my collar,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.57,0:39:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,上了车后  就开车\NI got in the car, and I started driving.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.21,0:39:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道该去哪\NHad no idea where to
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.41,0:39:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,直到我停在这个用木条封起的教堂\Nuntil I pulled up to this boarded-up church.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.85,0:39:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,相邻的那间教堂\NThis church right next door.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.68,0:39:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,而屋外的阶梯上站着\NAnd on the front steps was this
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.82,0:39:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,这美丽的女人\Nbeautiful woman
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.46,0:39:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,手握一瓶摩根船长威士忌\Nclutching onto a bottle of Captain Morgan,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.02,0:39:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,她说  你是牧师吗?\Nand she said, "You the reverend?"
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.46,0:39:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我说  是的我是\NAnd I said, "I am a reverend."
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.00,0:39:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,她又说  我一直在等你\NAnd she said, "I've been waiting on you."
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.77,0:39:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,现在  镇上的人们\NNow, folks in this town,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.94,0:39:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,他们都说是我救了Lettie Mae\Nthey say I saved Lettie Mae Thornton,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.28,0:39:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,说没有我  她不可能活\Nthat without me, she wouldn't be alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.75,0:39:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,但似乎没人理解\NBut what no one seems to understand
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.15,0:40:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,是那个女人救了我\Nis that that woman saved me
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.45,0:40:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,正如我救了她一样\Nevery bit as much as I saved her.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.79,0:40:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你好了吗？\NYou done?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.93,0:40:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉\NSorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.10,0:40:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你没必要道歉的\NYou have nothing to apologize for,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.70,0:40:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,所以别再道歉了\Nso stop apologizing.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.77,0:40:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,好\NOkay.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.04,0:40:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你注意到屋里没有酒精饮料吗\NYou notice there's no liquor in this house.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.24,0:40:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,恩\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.31,0:40:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,那是因为我妻子是个好人\NThat's because my wife is a good person,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.41,0:40:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,真的是个好人\Na deeply good person.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.58,0:40:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,但她得了一种疾病\NBut she's got a disease.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.88,0:40:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,一种没有区别的疾病\NIt's a disease that don't discriminate.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.92,0:40:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,就像是老鼠  什么都吃\NIt's like a rat. It'll eat whatever--
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.99,0:40:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,酒精  药片  赌博  性交…\Nbooze, pills, gambling, sex...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.16,0:40:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,或是V血\Nor vampire blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.23,0:40:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你是个好女孩  Willa\NYou're a nice girl, Willa.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.83,0:40:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我在那本书中了解了你所有的过往\NAnd I read about all what you've been through in that book there.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.40,0:40:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,为此我感到非常遗憾\NAnd I am so very sorry for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.44,0:40:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,但对于Lettie Mae  你现在所见的\NBut to Lettie Mae, all you look like now
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.11,0:41:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,就像喝了那瓶威士忌\Nis a bottle of Captain Morgan.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.85,0:41:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能再让你待在这了\NI can't have you around here no more.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.52,0:41:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,她骗过你一次  就会再来一次\NShe manipulated you once and she'll do it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.89,0:41:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  我了解\NOkay, I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.32,0:41:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,那谁保护你们呢？\NWho's gonna protect you?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.33,0:41:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,上帝会的  亲爱的  一如既往\NGod will, darlin'. Just like He always has.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.00,0:41:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,祝你好运\NGood luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.07,0:41:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你  Willa Burrell\NThank you, Willa Burrell,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.03,0:41:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你所做的一切\Nfor everything you've done.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.24,0:41:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,但我收回对你的邀请\NBut I rescind your invitation from this house.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.62,0:41:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿  伙计\NHey, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.96,0:41:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Lafayette?\NLafayette?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.60,0:41:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Lafayette  拜托\NLafayette, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.47,0:42:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Lafayette  拜托  醒醒  老兄\NLafayette, come on. Wake up, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.77,0:42:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Lafayette  醒醒\NLafayette, wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.07,0:42:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你到底哪根筋不对啊？\NWhat the hell is your malfunction?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.81,0:42:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我以为你因为我嗑多了  - 怎么会\N- I thought you OD'd on me. - Never.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.61,0:42:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我说过的  我是专家\NI told you, I is a professional.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.95,0:42:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,看看你\NLook at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.35,0:42:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你担心我？\NYou worried about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.16,0:42:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我在你心里生根发芽了？\NAm I growing on you?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.72,0:42:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,哦  得了吧\NOh, shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.13,0:42:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,- 真可爱  - 别逗了\N- It's cute. - Stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.93,0:42:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,就是嘛\NIt is.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.87,0:42:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,让我治好你的脖子  然后我就得走了\NLet me fix your neck, and then I have to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.97,0:42:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  我不动\NOkay, I'm stopping.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.72,0:42:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你…  - 怎么？\N- Is you-- - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.79,0:42:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,要开发我吗?\NGrooving on me?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.97,0:43:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,听着  我 额\NLook, I, um--
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.80,0:43:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉  我肯定是误解你之类的\NI'm sorry. I must've misread you or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.27,0:43:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,不  你并没有误解什么\NNo, you didn't misread anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.57,0:43:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,只是…\NIt's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.34,0:43:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道的  我和Jessica在一起\Nyou know, I'm with Jessica.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.08,0:43:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,对\NAll right.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.78,0:43:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我懂\NI gets it.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.06,0:43:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,晚安\NGood night.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.96,0:43:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,好眠  亲爱的\NNighty-night, lover.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.42,0:44:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Eric?\NEric?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.62,0:44:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我了个大去啊  Pam！\NJesus fucking Christ, Pam!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.46,0:44:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了？\NNow what?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.29,0:44:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会说  Northman先生\NI wouldn't, Mr. Northman.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.69,0:44:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你远比自己所想的寡不敌众\NYou're more outnumbered than you are aware.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.50,0:44:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你叫什么  姑娘？\NWhat's your name, girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.20,0:44:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H00FFFF&\fn楷书\fs24\pos(364,44)}Eric  我不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.72,0:44:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H00FFFF&\fn楷书\fs24\pos(364,44)}一切都不会有事的
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.83,0:44:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H00FFFF&\fn楷书\fs24\pos(364,44)}就是个威胁  仅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.29,0:44:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H00FFFF&\fn楷书\fs24\pos(364,44)}如果他们要杀了我们
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.32,0:44:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H00FFFF&\fn楷书\fs24\pos(364,44)}早动手了
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.35,0:45:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H00FFFF&\fn楷书\fs24\pos(364,44)}告诉他你的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:45:01.65,0:45:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Sylvie\NSylvie.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:05.02,0:45:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,恩  Sylvie\NMm, Sylvie.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.46,0:45:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,相当漂亮\NSo very pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:12.55,0:45:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H00FFFF&\fn楷书\fs24\pos(364,44)}拿下她
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.60,0:45:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Northman先生\NMan: Mr. Northman.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.07,0:45:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Eric!\NEric!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:24.41,0:45:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,谁派你来的？\NWho sent you?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.98,0:45:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我们是代表Yokonomo公司\NWe are here at the Yokonomo Corporation's behest.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:32.58,0:45:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,那么  好  告诉他们说我懂了\NWell, then, tell them I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.42,0:45:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,他们要表达的也表达了\NThey've made their point.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:37.79,0:45:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我未来会更加谨慎的  我保证\NI will be more careful in the future, I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:42.03,0:45:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你得做个选择  Northman先生\NYou have a choice to make, Mr. Northman.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.86,0:45:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,其中一人非死不可\NOne of them has to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.33,0:45:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你来选\NYou pick.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:53.37,0:45:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,- 动手吧  - 不\N- Do it  - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:54.74,0:45:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,停  停！\NStop, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.11,0:45:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Eric!\NEric!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.58,0:46:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  你们想怎样？\NOkay, what do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.95,0:46:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,钱？  我有钱\NMoney? I got money.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:05.68,0:46:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,他们付你多少  我都双倍奉上\NWhat are they paying you? I'll double it.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.65,0:46:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,三倍也行\NI will triple it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:10.32,0:46:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你是个富裕的人\NYou're a wealthy man,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:12.62,0:46:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,但你却不是公司\Nbut you are no corporation.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.49,0:46:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,,选吧\NChoose.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.26,0:46:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我很抱歉  Eric\NI'm so sorry, Eric.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:22.77,0:46:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我\NMe.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:24.30,0:46:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,不\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:25.94,0:46:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,杀了我\NKill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.64,0:46:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我恐怕  当局希望你活着\NThe Authority wants you alive, I'm afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:43.02,0:46:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Pam\NPam.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:49.06,0:46:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,放了Pam\NPam lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:10.47,0:47:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H00FFFF&\fn楷书\fs24\pos(364,44)}我们走
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.44,0:47:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H00FFFF&\fn楷书\fs24\pos(364,44)}天就快亮了
Dialogue: 0,0:47:18.62,0:47:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你是故意接触病毒的吗?\NDid you contract the virus on purpose?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:21.36,0:47:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,故意  不是\NOn purpose, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:24.29,0:47:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,难道我还要用\NBut did I go about my dealings
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.00,0:47:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,鬼在乎的态度来过日子？\Nwith a devil-may-care attitude?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:29.07,0:47:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,当然不\NAbsolutely.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:35.91,0:47:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你不能放弃  Eric\NYou can't give up, Eric.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.58,0:47:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,现在有充足的血液供给\NWith an ample blood supply,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:39.94,0:47:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,得病的吸血鬼能活得更久\Nvampires are living longer and longer with this disease.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:43.15,0:47:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,谁知道他们是否在研发解药\NAnd who knows, they're working on a cure.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:46.08,0:47:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,他们很快就会研发了\NThey could have one soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:48.75,0:47:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,求你了\NPlease.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.26,0:47:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我会帮你维持  直到…\NI will help keep you well until--
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.39,0:47:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么？\NWhy?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.39,0:48:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你真的后悔那晚你的选择吗？\NDo you regret the choice you made that night?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.00,0:48:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我做了唯一能做的选择\NI made the only choice I could.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:03.00,0:48:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,那就别逼我目睹\NThen don't make me watch this.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.24,0:48:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,- 别逼我目睹  - 我早就放你走了\N- Don't make me watch - I released you some time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:07.32,0:48:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,像你目睹Godric…\Nas you had to watch Godric...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:08.44,0:48:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,- 目睹Nora… - 你该走了\N- ...as you had to watch Nora. - You're free to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:11.04,0:48:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,别这样对我\NDo not do this to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:14.14,0:48:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,该死的\NGod damn you.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:20.55,0:48:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,千余年来  世界如我口中蚌肉\NFor more than 1,000 years, the world has been my oyster.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:24.05,0:48:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,如今也是\NAnd it still can be.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:27.56,0:48:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我愿做任何事\NI'll do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.93,0:48:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我已失去一切喜好  Pam\NI've lost my taste for oysters, Pam.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:33.73,0:48:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,不\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:38.44,0:48:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你该走了\NYou should go.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:00.12,0:49:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Sarah Newlin\NSarah Newlin.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:02.63,0:49:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,她怎么了？\NWhat about her?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.83,0:49:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我告诉你Jason Stackhouse放了她呢？\NWhat if I told you Jason Stackhouse let her live?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:11.20,0:49:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他没有  - 他有\N- He didn't. - He did.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:14.40,0:49:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,她就在外面\NAnd she's out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:16.21,0:49:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,- 哪里？ - 没人见过她\N- Where? - No one's seen her.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:18.48,0:49:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我想她是躲起来了\NI have to imagine she's in hiding somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:40.13,0:49:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,哇噢  那我们就去找到她\NWell, let's go find her.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:42.60,0:49:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,可以吗？\NShall we?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:56.41,0:49:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,屏住呼吸  Noomi\NHold your breath with me, Noomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:00.62,0:50:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要气息一致  一起极乐\NWe breathe together, we climax together.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:14.70,0:50:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,（合十礼）太棒了\NNamaste.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:30.65,0:50:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,哦  Noomi  Noomi  Noomi\NOh, Noomi, Noomi, Noomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:34.45,0:50:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Sanbir啊  Sanbir啊  Sanbir啊\NSanbir, Sanbir, Sanbir.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:40.52,0:50:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我把那当作是毕生事业\NI have made it my life's work
Dialogue: 0,0:50:43.69,0:50:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,将迷失的灵魂引领回正规\Nto steer lost souls onto the path.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:46.56,0:50:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我从未想到会有一个学员\NNot once did it occur to me that along would come a student...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:53.44,0:50:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,能够如此全面  多方位地\Nwho could so wholly and completely
Dialogue: 0,0:50:57.44,0:50:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,释放我\Nset me free.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:01.51,0:51:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你也让我能完全释放  大师\NYou make me whole and free, too, Guru.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:05.25,0:51:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,在我五个月前步入这个机构\NI walked into this institute five months ago
Dialogue: 0,0:51:09.95,0:51:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,一个迷茫的基督教女人\Na clueless Christian woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:13.92,0:51:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,名为Noomi…\Nnamed Noomi...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:16.96,0:51:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,笃信人世间的光阴\Nwho believed that life on Earth
Dialogue: 0,0:51:19.43,0:51:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,只是跨入天堂前的历练\Nwas just an audition to get into Heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:22.37,0:51:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我从不知道世间也能如沐天堂\NI never knew that life on Earth could be Heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:27.67,0:51:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,没有什么天堂  Noomi\NThere is no Heaven, Noomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:30.41,0:51:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,只有当下\NThere is only the now.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:35.48,0:51:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,当下即是人偶\NAnd now be a doll and go pick out
Dialogue: 0,0:51:38.88,0:51:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,去酒窖挑一瓶好酒吧\Na nice bottle of red from the cellar
Dialogue: 0,0:51:41.52,0:51:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我去准备阿育吠陀泡沫浴\Nwhile I draw us an Ayurvedic foaming bath,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:44.72,0:51:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,可以吗？\Nwill you?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:46.32,0:51:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,好的  大师\NYes, Guru.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:33.84,0:52:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,啊！  啊！\NAh! Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:36.77,0:52:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你是谁？  你想要什么？\NWho are you? What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:43.65,0:52:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你认识这女人吗？\NDo you know this woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:45.75,0:52:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,她的名字是Sarah Newlin\NHer name is Sarah Newlin.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:48.15,0:52:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我们有理由相信她就在这儿\NWe have reason to believe she is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:52.59,0:52:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能说谎\NI cannot tell a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:54.96,0:52:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,是的  我知道她\NYes, I know her.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:00.33,0:53:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,她在哪儿？\NWhere is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:04.60,0:53:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,这个我不能告诉你\NThis I will not tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:07.90,0:53:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,那你还真是没用\NHow very unhelpful of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:14.84,0:53:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,动手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:53:18.88,0:53:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Sarah Newlin!\NSarah Newlin!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:36.60,0:53:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Sookie  有人\NSookie, human.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:41.37,0:53:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,- 哦  我的天啊  Holly - 嘿  你在这儿啊\N- Oh, my God, Holly. - Hey there.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:44.31,0:53:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,哦  我的天\NOh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:46.58,0:53:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你去哪儿了？ - 我不知道\N- Where have you been? - I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:49.98,0:53:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,- Sookie！  - Bill！\N- Sookie! - Bill!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:56.45,0:53:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,抓着这女的了！  拿下他！\NWe got the girl! Take him out!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:01.96,0:54:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,去你的！\NFuck you!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:14.00,0:54:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,- 都在这儿了？ - 我想是的\N- That all of 'em? - Jason: I think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:16.74,0:54:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你他妈在想什么啊  Sookie？\NWhat the fuck were you thinking, Sookie?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:18.94,0:54:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,别回答我  别他妈说话  好吗？\NDon't answer me. Do not fuckin' talk, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:21.81,0:54:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你有吞下任何血吗？\NYou swallow any blood?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:23.55,0:54:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,眼睛呢？进眼睛了吗？\NWhat about your eyes? You get any in your eyes?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:25.52,0:54:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,点头Yes  摇头No\NJust shake your head yes or no.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:27.68,0:54:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,靠！帮我带她去河里洗洗\NFuck! Help me wash her off in the river.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:30.32,0:54:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我来\NI'm on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:31.69,0:54:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你\NYou.
